The '''Shop''' is a [[Main Menu]] page where users can purchase content from VRChat, or from the community. Content can be purchased with [[VRChat Credits]], and the types of content ranges from avatars, [[Creator Economy#Listings|listings]] from world & group [[Creator Economy#Stores|stores]], and listings which include content types from the [[Inventory]].

==Types of content==
Content that can appear in the store include:
* Inventory content
** [[Emojis|Emoji]]
** [[Stickers]]
** [[Items]]
** [[Inventory#Cosmetics|Cosmetics]]
*** [[Portals]]
*** [[Camera Drone|Drones]]
*** [[Warp Effects]]

* Avatars from the [[Avatar Marketplace]]
* World stores
* Group stores

==VRChat Store==
The VRChat Store is where VRChat sells content from themselves, which are limited to Inventory content types. They are offered as listings, each listing has products which include are the type of content the user will receive. Listings can be free, or purchased with VRChat Credits, and could be available for a limited amount of time.

===Gifting===
When selecting a listing, users are able to gift it instead of buying it for themselves. It may be done by clicking the gift button. When gifting, users will be able to choose to gift to a user within the instance or from their friends list. Note that while you may be able to choose users within the instance, you will only be able to gift to a friend. Users may only gift listings from the Shop if they reach the [[Trust Rank]] "User"

===Shelves===
Shelves are how the store is organized, each shelf is curated to a specific focus, such as a set of listings for an event or an update. 

===VRC+ discounts===
Listings offered in the shop are discounted if a user is subscribed to [[VRC+]]. These are indicated with a "{{Credits|}} with VRC+" line underneath the original price.

